quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  14,28,"E a tinaali …ďen wa…ótitir…ďe neemaaji Alla …óin keeferaaku, …ďe weerni yim…ďe …ďen galle halkaare"
  14,29,"Jahannama, hi…ďe naata nge, nge bonii √Īii…ďirde"
  14,30,"∆Āe wa…óani Alla yerondiraa…ói fii yo …ďe majjin (yim…ďe …ďen) e laawol Alla ngol. Maaku: \"Dakmitee, pellet ruttorde mon nden ko ka Yiite"
  14,31,"Maakan jeyaa…ďe am gom…óim…ďe …ďen, yo …ďe √Īinnu julde …ďe wintoo e kon ko Men arsiki …ďe gunndoo e kene, ado nde arata …ďe √Īalaande nde jgeeygu alaa e mun wanaa weldigal"
  14,32,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi, O jippiniri ka kammu ndiyam; O yaltiniri …óam dim…óe arsike wonannde on. O eltirani on laa…óe …óen, fii yo …óe dogir ka maayo e duŇčayee Makko. O eltani on kadi can…ói …óin"
  14,33,O eltani on naange ngen e lewru ndun dogooji …ói…ói. O eltani on jemma on e √Īalorma on
  14,34,"O okki on e kala ko tori…óon Mo. Si on lintii neemaaji Alla …óin, on moftataa…ói. Pellet ne…ó…óanke on ko hee- wu…óo too√Īe, heewu…óo yeddugol"
  14,35,"(Janto) kadi tuma nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"Joomi am, wa…óu ndee saare hooliinde, da…óndaa lam e …ďi…ó…ďe am …ďen nde men rewata sanamuuji"
  14,36,"Joomi am, kannji (sanamuuji …óin), …ói majjinii ko …óuu…ói e yim…ďe …ďen. Kala jokku…óo lam, on …óon ko jeyidaa…óo e am. Kala non yeddu…óo lam, haray An ko A Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  14,37,"Joomi amen, min mi ho…óinii yoga e …ďi…ó…ďe am …ďen e aynde nde wonaa remotoonde, ka Suudu Maa Hormanteeru, - Joomi amen - fii yo …ďe √Īinnu julde. Wa…óu …ďer…óe yim…ďe …ďen no yiiloo e ma…ď…ďe, arsikaa…ďe dim…óe, belajo'o …ďe yetta"
  14,38,"Joomi amen, pellet, An hi…óa anndi ko men suu…ói e ko men fe√Ī√Īini: hay huunde suu…óotaako Alla ka leydi wanaa ka kammu"
  14,39,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ye…óu…óo lam e hoore mawngu, Ismaa'iila e Ishaaqa. Pellet, Joomi am ko nanoowo du'aa"
  14,40,"Joomi am, wa…óan √Īinnoowo julde e …ďeynugol am ngol. Joomi amen, ja…ďu toraare am nden"
  14,41,"Joomi amen, haforanam min e jibim…ďe lam …ďen e gom…óim…ďe …ďen, √Īalnde √Īaawoore nden dorotoo"
  14,42,"Wata sikku Alla ko welsindii…óo e ko too√Īoo…ďe …ďen huuwata. Anndu ko O nenniranta …ďe, ko haa e √Īalaande nde gite saafotoo e mun"
  14,43,"Ko …ďe he√Īii…ďe, Ňčallim…ďe ko'e ma…ď…ďe, ndaar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yiltotaako e ma…ď…ďe, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko yeewu…óe"
  14,44,"Jertniri yim…ďe …ďen √Īalaande nde lepte …óen arata …ďe, too√Īu…ďe …ďen wi'a: \"Joomi amen, nennan men haa lajal …ďa…óiingal, men nootoo noddaanndu Maa, men jokka Nulaa…ďe …ďen\". E on laatanooki on woondiino ado (hannde) alanaa on iwugol (ton)"
  14,45,"Ho…óu…óon e ko…óooli …ďen too√Īu…ďe ko'e mun. ∆Āanngani on ko honno Men huuwunoo …ďe, Men piyani on mise"
  14,46,"Gom…óii …ďe fewjii feere ma…ď…ďe nden. Ko ka Alla feere ma…ď…ďe nden woni, hay si feere ma…ď…ďe nden ittayno pelle …óen"
  14,47,"Wata a sikku Alla ko lunndotoo…óo fodoore Makko (nde O fodi) Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo, Jom yottagol"
  14,48,"√Īalnde leydi ndin wa…ótitirtee leydi goo, e kammuuli …óin, …ďe fee√Īana Alla, Bajjo On, Foolu…óo On"
  14,49,"A yi'ay bom…ďe …ďen nden √Īalnde, ko jokkindiraa…ďe e kolombooje"
  14,50,"Dolokkaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin ko mbullam feewnira, Yiite ngen no sudda geece ma…ď…ďe …óen"
  14,51,"Fii yo Alla yo…ďitu kala wonkii ko ko faggitii. Pellet, Alla ko yaawu…óo hasboore"
  14,52,"Ndee (Alqur'aanaare) ko yottinoore yim…ďe …ďen fii yo …ďe waajitornde, e yo…ďe anndu kadi, wonnde Kanko ko O rewetee…óo Gooto, e fii yo joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji …ďen waajitor"